Detailed Description

Container for the outputs read from the INA for a given voltage rail.

Field Documentation

uint32_t pmhalIna226OutputData::busVoltage

Voltage at which the voltage domain is operating. The voltage value is represented in micro Volts

int32_t pmhalIna226OutputData::current

Current drawn in micro amperes

int32_t pmhalIna226OutputData::power

Power drawn in micro watts

uint32_t pmhalIna226OutputData::shuntRes

Shunt resistance along the given voltage rail

int32_t pmhalIna226OutputData::shuntVoltage

Voltage accross the shunt resistor. The voltage value is in nano Volts

pmhalPrcmPmicRegulatorId_t pmhalIna226OutputData::voltDomId

Voltage Domain for the data. Refer to pmhalPrcmPmicRegulatorId_t for valid values.
